<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<section class="page-header" style="padding-bottom:56px;">
  <span class="eyebrow">Results</span>
  <h1 class="display">Results you<br>can measure.</h1>
  <p class="lede" style="max-width:620px;">We don&rsquo;t sell promises. We sell sharper brands, stronger visibility, hours saved, and share of voice &mdash; the numbers that turn attention into real client conversations.</p>
</section>

<section class="container" style="padding:20px 24px 20px;">
  <div class="featured-case" style="align-items:center;">
    <div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:16px;">Featured &middot; B2B SaaS</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(48px,8vw,88px);letter-spacing:-0.04em;color:var(--accent);line-height:0.95;margin-bottom:16px;">+310%</div>
      <h2 style="margin:0 0 14px;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(24px,3.4vw,32px);letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.1;">AI citations in 90 days</h2>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--text-muted);max-width:460px;">We made a B2B SaaS brand the default recommendation across four answer engines — closing every priority citation gap and turning that presence into a pipeline of qualified conversations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-seam grid-seam--stat">
      <div class="stat-cell" style="padding:26px;"><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text);">4</div><div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.5;">Answer engines won</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell" style="padding:26px;"><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text);">#1</div><div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.5;">Share of voice in category</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell" style="padding:26px;"><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text);">90d</div><div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.5;">To measurable lift</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell" style="padding:26px;"><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text);">2.4x</div><div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.5;">Qualified inbound</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container" style="padding:22px 24px 90px;">
  <div class="grid-seam grid-seam--auto-fill">
    <div style="padding:34px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;min-height:230px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-faint);">Branding</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:40px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:var(--accent);line-height:1;">Full rebrand</div>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text-muted);flex:1;">A new identity and website that finally matched the quality of the work &mdash; and doubled qualified inbound.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:34px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;min-height:230px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-faint);">Automation &amp; AI</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:40px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:var(--accent);line-height:1;">20 hrs/wk</div>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text-muted);flex:1;">Automated manual operations so a lean team could spend its time on clients, not busywork.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:34px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;min-height:230px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-faint);">AI Search</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:40px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:var(--accent);line-height:1;">Cited #1</div>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text-muted);flex:1;">Became the lead-cited source for &ldquo;best-in-category&rdquo; buyer prompts across ChatGPT and Perplexity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band section--top-border">
  <div class="cta-band__inner">
    <h2>Your brand could be next.</h2>
    <p>Let&rsquo;s baseline your visibility and build the plan to own the answer.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book a strategy call</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
